{"tid":386221,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係下列兩類人，而會考無五科合格，或者無一門手藝嘅都係垃圾","createTime":"2017-09-03T17:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T04:19:09.000Z","uid":15495,"like":13,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"32f76f6a2124a5aa69b5ada22980a2b1342a54d9","tid":386221,"uid":15495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:00:25.000Z","msg":"1. 屋企經濟環境極差，要好早出黎做野<br />\n2. 讀寫障礙 或者其他身體/精神上嘅毛病<br />\n<br />\n老老實實，政府都用公帑供你讀左十幾年書，十幾年你連五科合格都拎唔到，都算，當你真係唔啱讀書，咁你去學廚，學美容，學剪髮，學電機，都係一門手藝，你連呢幾瓣 Practical 嘅野都學唔掂，書又讀唔黎，不如死左佢算啦。"},{"pid":"cfbf9f2a0c51c371d19c2e6f6d6be5703fdc73b9","tid":386221,"uid":106506,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:15:40.000Z","msg":"寧欺白鬚公 莫欺少年窮<br />\n你條柒頭點知人地 可能未搵到啱自己發圍個範啫<br />\n留名等睇樓主幾時仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc157ce9d2a87ad4835a0fdfc67ab92ca034f28a","tid":386221,"uid":15495,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T18:10:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寧欺白鬚公 莫欺少年窮<br />\n你條柒頭點知人地 可能未搵到啱自己發圍個範啫<br />\n留名等睇樓主幾時仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做成廿年人，一啲自己嘅長處都搵唔到？"},{"pid":"345db918588361ee264840975328e955119d59d4","tid":386221,"uid":106506,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T18:14:04.000Z","msg":"唔出奇 有人思想早熟 有人遲熟<br />\n後來追上嘅大有人在"},{"pid":"1c2f393469f9ff4a280799f6c255d91eeefa5ad6","tid":386221,"uid":78295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T01:20:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寧欺白鬚公 莫欺少年窮<br />\n你條柒頭點知人地 可能未搵到啱自己發圍個範啫<br />\n留名等睇樓主幾時仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf33bd341234db3f799b7ffe5c1a0641820b09b1","tid":386221,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T01:28:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /